<HEADLINE>
FT  14 APR 94 / People: Non-executive appointments
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Donald Chilvers, a former partner of Coopers &amp; Lybrand who formed its
forensic accounting group, as chairman of MERRETT Underwriting Agency
Management.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
